lacelang-testkit (0.1.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Bundles conformance vectors and reference mock HTTP server.
  * Supports both `-c <cmd>` direct invocation and `-m <manifest.toml>`
    templated invocation for executors with complex command shapes.
  * Reporter formats: text, TAP, JUnit XML.

 -- lacelang contributors <maintainers@lacelang.dev>  Wed, 15 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000
